〈'''How You Like That'''〉是韩国女子组合[[BLACKPINK|BLACKPINK]]于2020年6月26日发布的单曲，是该组合首张正规韩语专辑《[[THE_ALBUM_(BLACKPINK專輯)|THE ALBUM]]》的先导单曲，该专辑于2020年10月2日发行。歌曲由[[泰迪·朴|泰迪·朴]]及Danny Chung共同创作，泰迪·朴、{{tsl|en|R. Tee|R·Tee}}和24共同制作<ref>{{citeweb|title=BLACKPINK Reveals Credit Poster For ‘How You Like That’, Participation From TEDDY|url=https://yg-life.com/archives/156429?lang=en|date=2020-06-22|accessdate=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929035925/https://yg-life.com/archives/156429?lang=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 歌曲融合[[流行_(音乐类型)|流行]]、[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈]]及[[EDM_Trap|陷阱]]元素，教导人们“不要被黑暗的情况吓倒，失去再度站起来的自信和力量”。

随附音乐视频由徐贤成执导，歌曲发行当天同步上线Blackpink的[[YouTube|YouTube]]频道，一上线便打破YouTube多项纪录，包括首播视频观看人数最多的视频、[[發布後24小時內觀看次數最多的網路影片列表|发布后24小时内观看人数最多的视频]]（期间共计8630万次）、点击量破1亿、2亿和6亿最快的视频、[[最受喜歡的YouTube視頻列表|点赞人数最多的视频]]（1700多万赞）。音樂錄音帶歷時504天，於2021年11月12日突破10億觀看次數，成為BLACKPINK最快突破10億觀看次數的音樂錄音帶<ref>{{Cite news|last=@BLACKPINK|url=https://twitter.com/BLACKPINK/status/1458983586502045697?t=WscckUYV5Wm-i5h4pO1KWg&s=19|title=BLACKPINK 'How You Like That' M/V HITS 1 BILLION VIEWS|newspaper=twitter|accessdate=2021-11-12|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211114131007/https://twitter.com/blackpink/status/1458983586502045697?t=WscckUYV5Wm-i5h4pO1KWg&s=19}}</ref>。

歌曲获[[2020年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2020年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]{{tsl|en|MTV Video Music Award for Song of Summer|MTV音乐录影带大奖最佳夏日歌曲|最佳夏日歌曲}}奖、{{tsl|en|2020 Melon Music Awards|2020年Melon音乐大奖}}最佳女性舞蹈奖及[[2020年Mnet亚洲音乐大奖|2020年Mnet亚洲音乐大奖]]最佳女子组合舞蹈表演奖。商业成绩方面，歌曲登陆26国榜单，其中在韩国（Gaon榜和韩流百强单曲榜）、新加坡、匈牙利和马来西亚夺冠<ref>{{cite web|url=https://micky.com.au/blackpink-almost-smashed-kanye-west-travis-scott-sales/|title=Blackpink almost smashed Kanye West, Travis Scott sales|date=2020-07-07|accessdate=2020-07-31|work=Micky|first=Mike|last=Pantoja-Contreras|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711124942/https://micky.com.au/blackpink-almost-smashed-kanye-west-travis-scott-sales/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，还获得加拿大金唱片销量认证及日本的银唱片销量认证，专辑版则获得韩国的铂金认证。

==背景与发行==
2020年5月4日，报道指BLACKPINK已完成新专辑的录制工作，计划在当月晚些时候拍摄一段音乐视频<ref>{{citeweb|title=[단독] 블랙핑크, 6월 컴백..YG "정확한 날짜 팬들에게"(종합)|url=https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2020050410445616469&VBC|last=Moon|first=Wan-sik|date=2020-05-04|website=Star News|language=ko|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616000827/https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2020050410445616469&VBC|archive-date=2020-06-16|accessdate=2020-06-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.rappler.com/entertainment/music/259853-blackpink-comeback-june-2020|title=BLACKPINK comeback scheduled in June 2020|last=|first=|magazine=Rappler|accessdate=2020-06-16|date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200601031235/https://www.rappler.com/entertainment/music/259853-blackpink-comeback-june-2020|archive-date=2020-06-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月18日，[[YG娱乐|YG娱乐]]更新计划动态，透露2020年6月将有一个新作品公布，同时表示组合的首张正规专辑将有超过10首歌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ygent_official/status/1262205839953166336|title=#BLACKPINK 정규 앨범에 대하여|date=2020-05-18|accessdate=2020-06-16|publisher=YG Family|via=Twitter|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518022003/https://twitter.com/ygent_official/status/1262205839953166336|archive-date=2020-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sports.donga.com">{{cite web|url=https://sports.donga.com/article/all/20200518/101093085/1|title=블랙핑크 측 "첫 정규앨범 작업 끝…오는 9월 발표 예정" [공식]|website=Sports Dongha|accessdate=2020-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610050005/https://sports.donga.com/article/all/20200518/101093085/1|archive-date=2020-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月10日，YG娱乐在社交媒体发布单曲的先导海报，确认组合于6月26日回归<ref>{{Cite web|last=Ent|first=Y. G.|title=BLACKPINK – COMEBACK TEASER POSTER|url=https://yg-life.com/archives/155958?lang=en|access-date=2020-06-10|website=YG LIFE|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616185705/https://yg-life.com/archives/155958?lang=en|archive-date=2020-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Mamo |first1=Heran |title=Everything We Know About Blackpink's Highly-Anticipated Comeback Single |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9399948/blackpink-comeback-single-announcement |website=Billboard |accessdate=2020-07-16 |date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704064227/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9399948/blackpink-comeback-single-announcement |archive-date=2020-07-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。三天后，YG娱乐发布组合全新真人秀节目《24/365 with BLACKPINK》的序章，该节目于6月4日在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上线<ref>{{cite tweet|user=BLACKPINK |number=1278157494712328192 |date=2020-07-01 |title=24/365 with Blackpink teaser poster}} </ref>。节目记录了组合回归的过程，分享她们日常的[[vlog|vlog]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202006131006105562067_1|title=블랙핑크, 새 단독 리얼리티 론칭…팬들과 적극 소통한다|website=Herald Pop|language=ko|access-date=2020-06-13|date=2020-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613011715/http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202006131006105562067_1|archive-date=2020-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。成员[[金智秀_(歌手)|智秀]]在序章中表示，新歌会摆脱之前的“强劲”风格，更加“炫酷”<ref>{{cite web|title=24/365 with Blackpink prologue|URL=https://youtube.com/watch?v=ZjGiK87EaQ0|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628015533/https://youtube.com/watch?v=ZjGiK87EaQ0|archive-date=2020-06-28|accessdate=2020-07-02|work=YouTube}}</ref>。

6月15日，YG娱乐发布成员个人海报<ref name="#2">{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=1272317949110452224|date=2020-06-15 |title=#BLACKPINK 'How You Like That' TITLE POSTER}}</ref>。翌日，全新先导海报首次透露单曲名称为〈How You Like That〉<ref name="#2"/>，而成员亮相的概念视频于6月18日和19日发布<ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=HHwWgsCnwaLOhawjAAAA|date=2020-06-18 |title=How You Like That' ROSÉ Concept Teaser Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=HHwWgICmiarUhawjAAAA|date=2020-06-18 |title=How You Like That' JENNIE Concept Teaser Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=HHwWgMCrlaKzqq0jAAAA|date=2020-06-19 |title=How You Like That' LISA Concept Teaser Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=HHwWgsCgzb3Lr60jAAAA|date=2020-06-19 |title=How You Like That' JISOO Concept Teaser Video}}</ref> ，翌日概念照公布<ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=HHwWgMCjqaqZz64jAAAA|date=2020-06-20 |title=How You Like That' TITLE POSTER}}</ref>，隔日先导视频公布<ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=1274492307216011264|date=2020-06-21 |title=How You Like That'  Concept Teaser Video}}</ref>。 组合官方先导海报于6月22日公布<ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=1274854649619599360|date=2020-06-22 |title=How You Like That' CREDIT POSTER}}</ref>。音乐视频抢先版于6月24日发布<ref>{{cite tweet |user=ygent_official |number=1275579451816808448|date=2020-06-24 |title=How You Like That' M/V TEASER}}</ref>。6月26日，经过一小时的倒计时暖场节目，歌曲正式上线<ref>{{cite web |title=[Replay] BLACKPINK ‘How You Like That’ COUNTDOWN LIVE‘How You Like That’ COUNTDOWN LIVE |url=https://www.vlive.tv/video/198945 |website=Vlive |accessdate=2020-07-16 |date=2020-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626082908/https://www.vlive.tv/video/198945 |archive-date=2020-06-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歌曲的CD单曲于7月27日发行，内附伴奏<ref name="CD">{{cite web|url=http://en.ygselect.com/Product/Detail/view/pid/5642/cid/1682|title=BLACKPINK SPECIAL EDITION [How You Like That]|publisher=YG Select|date=2020-06-28|accessdate=2020-07-19|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200720081929/http://en.ygselect.com/Product/Detail/view/pid/5642/cid/1682|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

