nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL|website=gaonchart.co.kr|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309051712/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL|archive-date=2017-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在巴西，歌曲打破2020年外语歌曲的流媒体记录，超越[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]和[[爱莉安娜·格兰德|爱莉安娜·格兰德]]的〈[[让雨降临|让雨降临]]〉。在这个拉丁地区最大的市场，歌曲成为2020年空降成绩第四高的作品，也创下韩国组合在该国的最好榜单成绩<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/chartdatab/status/1279904136331485184|title=Maiores debuts em streams no Brasil em 2020 (até agora):|date=2020-07-05|accessdate=2020-07-06|language=pt|work=União Brasileira de Compositores|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705223838/https://twitter.com/chartdatab/status/1279904136331485184|archive-date=2020-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在美国，歌曲与〈[[酸糖|酸糖]]〉一同空降[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]第33位，刷新韩国女艺人在该榜的最高纪录<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9414723/blackpink-how-you-like-that-five-burning-questions|title=Five Burning Questions: Blackpink Debut in the Top 40 With 'How You Like That'|work=Billboard|date=2020-07-07|accessdate=2020-08-12|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718084802/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9414723/blackpink-how-you-like-that-five-burning-questions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。发行首周及上榜两周共卖出16,400份<ref>{{cite web|last=Pantoja-Contreras|first=Mike|title=Blackpink almost smashed Kanye West, Travis Scott sales|url=https://micky.com.au/blackpink-almost-smashed-kanye-west-travis-scott-sales/|work=mickey|date=2020-07-07|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711124942/https://micky.com.au/blackpink-almost-smashed-kanye-west-travis-scott-sales/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/blackpink/chart-history/hot-100|title=Blackpink Chart History: Hot 100|work=Billboard|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520095019/https://www.billboard.com/music/blackpink/chart-history/hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外歌曲还跻身奥地利、加拿大、爱沙尼亚、匈牙利、新西兰、英国和苏格兰榜前20。

==音乐视频==
歌曲的音乐视频由徐贤成执导<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.promonews.tv/videos/2020/06/29/blackpink-how-you-seo-hyun-seung/65410|title=BLACKPINK 'How You Like That' by Seo Hyun-seung|website=Promonews|accessdate=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701075736/https://www.promonews.tv/videos/2020/06/29/blackpink-how-you-seo-hyun-seung/65410|archive-date=2020-07-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，徐賢成之前曾执导过〈[[Ddu-Du_Ddu-Du|Ddu-Du Ddu-Du]]〉和〈[[Kill_This_Love_(歌曲)|Kill This Love]]〉。视频凭借166万同时在线观看数，成为YouTube首播观看次数最多的音乐视频<ref name="bbc">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-53190589?utm_source=soldsie&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=200626_blackpink%3Ahowyoulikethatscoresthebiggestpremiereinyoutubehistory |title=Blackpink: How You Like That scores the biggest premiere in YouTube history |first=Mark |last=Savage |work=BBC News |accessdate=2020-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628051158/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-53190589?utm_source=soldsie&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=200626_blackpink%3Ahowyoulikethatscoresthebiggestpremiereinyoutubehistory |archive-date=2020-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。后来继续成为[[發布後24小時內觀看次數最多的網路影片列表|YouTube发布24小时内观看人数最多的视频]]，時間段內有8630萬次播放，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.naver.com/entertain/article/076/0003592162|title=블랙핑크, 유튜브 공식발표 24시간 조회수 8630만 '최초·최고·최대'…글로벌 파급력 [공식]|date=2020-06-30|first=|last=|work=Naver|accessdate=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630031746/https://news.naver.com/entertain/article/076/0003592162|archive-date=2020-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。视频也是YouTube史上播放量最快达到1亿的音乐视频，发布后约32小时便实现该记录<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20200628000063|title=BLACKPINK's 'How You Like That' becomes fastest video ever to top 100 million YouTube views|work=The Korea Herald|date=2020-06-28|accessdate=2020-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628140427/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20200628000063|archive-date=2020-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到2020年7月17日，视频上线三个星期，播放量超过3亿<ref>{{cite web |last1=Yoon |first1=So-yeon |title=Blackpink smashes its own record for fastest time to reach 300M views |url=https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2020/07/17/entertainment/kpop/Blackpink-How-You-Like-That-300-million-views/20200717190000419.html |website=Korea Joong Ang Daily |accessdate=2020-07-17 |date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717122044/https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2020/07/17/entertainment/kpop/Blackpink-How-You-Like-That-300-million-views/20200717190000419.html |archive-date=2020-07-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同时凭借1300万次赞，成为[[最受喜歡的YouTube視頻列表|最受喜歡的YouTube視頻]]，另外，该视频也在[[2020年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2020年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]上获得{{tsl|en|MTV Video Music Award for Song of Summer|MTV音乐录影带大奖最佳夏日歌曲|最佳夏日歌曲}}大奖<ref name="VMA2020" />。

然而，视频由于有影射印度[[象头神|象头神]]的镜头，在社交媒体引发风波。在涉事画面中，作为道具的象头神雕塑被放置在地面，许多歌迷认为这是[[文化挪用|文化挪用]]。有关画面后来被删走<ref>{{cite web|url=https://cnalifestyle.channelnewsasia.com/trending/statue-hindu-deity-removed-blackpink-video-how-you-like-that-12889290|title=Statue of Hindu deity removed from Blackpink’s record-smashing video after complaints|date=2020-07-01|work=CNA|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712074401/https://cnalifestyle.channelnewsasia.com/trending/statue-hindu-deity-removed-blackpink-video-how-you-like-that-12889290|archive-date=2020-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==奖项==
歌曲因创下24小时内观看次数最多的YouTube视频、24小时内观看次数最多的YouTube音乐视频、24小时内观看次数最多的YouTube韩国组合音乐视频、首播观看人数最多的YouTube视频、首播观看人数最多的YouTube音乐视频，被列入2020年[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]<ref name="Guinness"/>。

